"```sql\nSELECT c.name, l.format\nFROM cards c\nJOIN legalities l ON c.uuid = l.uuid\nWHERE c.edhrecRank = 1 AND l.status = 'Banned';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the names of cards that are ranked 1st on EDHRec and lists the play formats in which they are banned. It joins the `cards` table with the `legalities` table using the `uuid` foreign key relationship and filters the results based on the specified conditions."